      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity to get on the road at a great value! While it shows some honest signs of its travels and typical wear, it remains a dependable companion that's eager to keep going. It\u2019s the perfect choice for anyone seeking a solid, functional car without the premium price tag!",
