    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you\u2019re heading out on a road trip or just cruising around town, this car is super reliable and ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
