    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and reliability. Finished in a deep metallic gloss, the exterior has been meticulously cared for, showing only the lightest signs of road use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all onboard technology\u2014from the responsive navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine delivers consistent, smooth power, a testament to a life of diligent, on-time servicing. It drives straight, brakes sharply, and offers a quiet ride that speaks to its mechanical integrity. We have maintained a comprehensive folder of all service records, ensuring the next owner can drive away with total peace of mind. This is a refined, turn-key example ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
